# Production build-time env. On Vercel, set these in the project's
# Environment Variables dashboard — NOT in this file. This file is just
# documentation for what the prod build expects.
#
# VITE_API_BASE — full origin of the deployed backend on Render.
# Trailing slash is fine; the apiBase helper trims it.
VITE_API_BASE=https://rupeezy-voice-agent.onrender.com
